data.description: Welcome to this beautiful recently remodeled 3 bedroom 2 bathroom POOL home! The kitchen has quartz counters, soft close cabinets, stainless steel appliances and designer tile, lighting and flooring. Each room has it's own designer light/fan with wall mount control. The spacious master bedroom has a large walk in closet. This home features a split floor plan with practical layout and no wasted space. The sliding door opens from the family room to the spacious screened porch, perfect for entertaining. The garage features an opener. Don't miss this amazing opportunity to own a pool home of this quality. This home is located in a quiet neighborhood close to shopping, eateries, schools and hospitals. Disney attractions and beaches are all within an hours drive!! *This home is owner occupied*
